F_{Y|X=x}(y)= \int_{-∞}^{y} f_{Y|X=x} (z) dz
F_{Y|X=x}(y)= \frac{\int_{-∞}^{y} f_{X,Y} (z) dz}{\int_{-∞}^{∞} f_{X,Y} (z) dz}
